1. Clone the repository:
git clone https://github.com/YOUR_USERNAME/ML_tutor_chatbot.git
cd ML_tutor_chatbot

2. Make sure to download ollama model after cloning is done
follow requirements to understand on how to download after installing run ollama run mistral to check if the model is working by asking basic ML question in terminal.

3. Create local evev before going to next steps 
python3 -m venv venv
source venv/bin/activate   # Mac

4. run pip install -r requirements.txt in terminal streamlit will be installed in your laorop

5. before running streamlit get your model active using the following cmd
ollama serve

6. Run streamlit 
streamlit run app.py

7. when you are pushing remember to create a branch and send a merge request after removing venv from the folder